</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-e0f918913530e9b1 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container featured-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Monday Sit-at-home: Onerous Task for Anambra Gov, Security Agencies" href="../11/monday-sit-at-home-onerous-task-for-anambra-gov-security-agencies5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Anambra-State.gif" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-share"><amp-social-share layout="responsive" width="25" height="25" type="system" aria-label="Share" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de share-system i-amphtml-layout-responsive i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="responsive"><i-amphtml-sizer style="display:block;padding-top:100%"></i-amphtml-sizer></amp-social-share></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Monday Sit-at-home: Onerous Task for Anambra Gov, Security Agencies" href="../11/monday-sit-at-home-onerous-task-for-anambra-gov-security-agencies5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Monday Sit-at-home: Onerous Task for Anambra Gov, Security Agencies</h3></a></div></article></div></div></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 next-category-articles"><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 header"><span class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 title">Nigeria</span></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 container"><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Naira Sustains Gains, Now N1,382/$, Tinubu Canvasses Patronage of Local Goods" href="../23/naira-sustains-gains-now-n1382-tinubu-canvasses-patronage-of-local-goods5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="